---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — Departure: Fitness Quest">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative pt-16 pb-20 lg:pt-24 lg:pb-28 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary/8 via-bg to-bg pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-10 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-20 right-1/4 w-72 h-72 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 mb-6">
        <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-medium">Our Story</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-6">
        Where <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent">real fitness</span> meets
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-gold to-red">real gaming.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg sm:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        We got tired of choosing between a good workout tracker and a fun fitness app. So we built both.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem / Solution - Two Column -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <!-- The Problem -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 bg-red/90 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white">THE PROBLEM</div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-red/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-red/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Two bad options</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
              Most fitness apps fall into two camps: serious workout trackers that are boring as hell, or gamified fitness apps that don't actually track real workouts.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Spreadsheet-style trackers with zero motivation</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">"Do 50 pushups to defeat the goblin" gimmicks</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Anime aesthetics aimed at teenagers</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- The Solution -->
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 left-6 bg-green/90 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white">THE SOLUTION</div>
          <div class="bg-surface border border-green/20 rounded-2xl p-8 h-full">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">Departure</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
              Real workout tracking — sets, reps, weight, personal records, progressive overload — wrapped in an RPG that actually makes you want to open the app.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Full gym-grade workout logging with 88+ exercises</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Dark Souls-inspired aesthetic for adults</span>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-green mt-1 shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
                <span class="text-text-muted text-sm">Your bench press builds your STR and defeats the Kraken</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Differentiators -->
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">What makes Departure different</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">AI Future Self</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Upload a selfie, set your goals. AI generates what you could realistically look like. Not a filter — a target.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-red/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Anti-Cheat System</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">6-layer fraud detection: weight limits, spike detection, daily caps. Every rule is transparent. Honest effort only.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Real XP, Real Progress</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">XP comes from actual sets, reps, and effort — not arbitrary quests. Your rank reflects your real training.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Team-First Social</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Teams fight monsters together. Your workouts fuel combat power. React to teammates' sessions. Accountability built in.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Free to Play</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">No paywall. No subscriptions. No ads. Every feature works free. Premium is a boost, not a gate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="group bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 3v4M3 5h4M6 17v4m-2-2h4m5-16l2.286 6.857L21 12l-5.714 2.143L13 21l-2.286-6.857L5 12l5.714-2.143L13 3z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Dark Souls Aesthetic</h3>
          <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Built for adults. No anime. No cartoon characters. War banners, ancient monsters, and a world that takes fitness seriously.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Qualia AI Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-surface/30">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-5 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="lg:col-span-3">
          <span class="text-primary-light text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider">The Team</span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-2 mb-4">Built by Qualia AI</h2>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-4">
            Departure is built by <strong class="text-text">Qualia AI</strong>, a consulting firm that builds AI-powered products. We use the same tech we deploy for enterprise clients — computer vision, generative AI, real-time data processing — to make fitness more engaging.
          </p>
          <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">
            This isn't a side project. It's what happens when engineers who train decide to build the app they wish existed.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <a href="mailto:support@engagequalia.com" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary hover:bg-primary-light text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-sm transition-colors">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" /></svg>
              Get in Touch
            </a>
            <a href="https://engagequalia.com" class="text-text-muted hover:text-text text-sm font-medium transition-colors">
              engagequalia.com
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <div class="bg-surface border border-surface-light/50 rounded-2xl p-6">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-light" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-sm">AI-First Approach</p>
                  <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">Gemini-powered body transformation, generative art</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 20l4-16m4 4l4 4-4 4M6 16l-4-4 4-4" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-sm">Modern Stack</p>
                  <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">React Native, Supabase, Expo — built to scale</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gold/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
                  <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-gold" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z" /></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <p class="font-semibold text-sm">Privacy-First</p>
                  <p class="text-text-muted text-xs">No data selling, no ads, no tracking</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to start your quest?</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg mb-8">Free. No paywall. Just train.</p>
      <a href="/#notify" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-primary hover:bg-primary-light text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold transition-colors text-lg">
        Get Notified
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
